1
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:09,950
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,230
Nianzhao,

4
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,280
I hope you can fulfill my wish

5
00:01:17,570 --> 00:01:20,030
to bring peace and prosperity
to the people.

6
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,590
Li!

7
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,000
Li.

8
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,720
How did this happen?

9
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,710
It was the Empress Dowager.

10
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,650
What are you doing?

11
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,660
Don't move!

12
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,760
Don't worry,

13
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:10,430
you won't die just yet.

14
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,800
If Xie Jiuzhao cannot be executed today,

15
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:17,360
your life will be worthless anyway.

16
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,280
I'm sorry,

17
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,430
I'm sorry, Zhao.

18
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,590
I promised I wouldn't make you worry.

19
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,150
It's alright, Li.

20
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,079
It's alright.

21
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,360
Go find the antidote!

22
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,490
I'm going right now!

23
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,990
Zhao,

24
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:37,280
we were so close.

25
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:43,240
I really want to go back
to Chunliu Garden with you

26
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,460
and live a simple life.

27
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,360
Stop talking.

28
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,240
Hold on.

29
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,000
The antidote will be here soon.

30
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,400
When we return to Chunliu Garden,

31
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:56,030
we'll have our wedding ceremony

32
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:59,750
in front of my mother,

33
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,310
alright?

34
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:03,630
Alright. I promise you.

35
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,120
I promise.

36
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:07,910
Zhao,

37
00:03:08,810 --> 00:03:10,370
you're so good to me.

38
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:13,910
Li.

39
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,000
Li!

40
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,430
Li!

41
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,030
Li!

42
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:25,690
[Chunliu Garden]

43
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,750
[Spiritual Sound of Stone]

44
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,910
Li!

45
00:03:56,829 --> 00:04:00,140
[One year later]

46
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:02,430
I've heard that swans

47
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,750
are the most faithful birds in the world.

48
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,520
If one unfortunately dies,

49
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,780
the other will mourn and cry all day long.

50
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,240
I am your swan.

51
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,680
Oh, stop it.

52
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,850
Do you have any better paper
for making lanterns?

53
00:04:22,850 --> 00:04:23,480
Oh,

54
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,560
Young Master Zhao,

55
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,510
you've bought

56
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:27,070
so many kinds of paper this month.

57
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:29,000
Haven't you learned how to make it?

58
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,800
I just want to make the best one.

59
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:36,650
Are you planning to set up a stall
for the Lantern Festival?

60
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,270
My wife once said

61
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,880
that when she was little,

62
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,980
she always loved carrying a lantern
her mother made

63
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,590
to the Lantern Festival.

64
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,750
You're married?

65
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,120
How come I've never seen your wife?

66
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,830
This mask is quite unique.

67
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,190
Li.

68
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,480
May I help you, sir?

69
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,480
Sorry, I mistook you for someone else.

70
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,040
Zhao.

71
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:58,830
Zhao.

72
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:00,720
Zhao.

73
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:12,130
[Wenxiang Pavilion]

74
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,000
Li?

75
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,630
What are you thinking?

76
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:22,090
I called you so many times.

77
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:24,830
You're finally back.

78
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:35,040
What's wrong?

79
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:36,240
Look at you. Did you miss me?

80
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:40,020
♪ One last thread of longing ♪

81
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:43,120
♪ Forgetting what regret feels like ♪

82
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,750
You were gone for so long this time,

83
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,150
and you wouldn't let me come with you.

84
00:06:45,150 --> 00:06:46,680
♪ Letting time lie to us ♪

85
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,120
How could I not miss you?

86
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,900
I made it back in time.

87
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:50,510
♪ Turning over in the hands of fate ♪

88
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,040
Xi'er's hometown is so far away.

89
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,950
I should pay my respects there
every year no matter what.

90
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,600
♪ The past that lives in my heart ♪

91
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,360
We've just settled down.

92
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:58,610
If you had come with me,

93
00:06:58,610 --> 00:06:59,000
♪ Is your quiet unease ♪

94
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,200
who would have taken care of the garden?

95
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,950
Alright, come on.

96
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:03,170
Let's go home.

97
00:07:03,170 --> 00:07:05,100
♪ If life's answer ♪

98
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,120
♪ Is incomplete ♪

99
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:10,830
♪ Then let me walk what's left with you ♪

100
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:13,420
♪ Sandstorms filled the desert sky ♪

101
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:16,340
♪ Yet they never buried this ♪

102
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:20,060
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

103
00:07:20,550 --> 00:07:22,150
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

104
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:24,710
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

105
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:29,060
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

106
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:31,610
♪ You held the fire
you lit with your heart ♪

107
00:07:31,610 --> 00:07:32,080
[Chunliu Garden]

108
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:34,240
♪ And gave it to me without fear ♪

109
00:07:34,650 --> 00:07:35,710
♪ Even in the dead of night ♪

110
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:39,000
♪ That flash of light ♪

111
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:43,400
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

112
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:48,610
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

113
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:58,880
♪ The desert in the wilderness ♪

114
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:03,260
♪ You were there for me ♪

115
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:07,890
♪ The turbulent night ♪

116
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,630
♪ The intersection of life and death ♪

117
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,430
So beautiful.

118
00:08:12,550 --> 00:08:13,430
♪ The color of my dream ♪

119
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:14,750
My Li is so capable.

120
00:08:17,470 --> 00:08:21,570
♪ We fell in love with each other ♪

121
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,720
♪ I missed you so much ♪

122
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:25,040
♪ And I can't get you off my mind ♪

123
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,310
It's lovely.

124
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,160
♪ I can't breathe without you ♪

125
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,360
Where did you buy it?

126
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,750
I made it myself.

127
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:30,390
This is our first
Lantern Festival together.

128
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:32,200
♪ Sandstorms filled the desert sky ♪

129
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:32,590
Of course I...

130
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:35,289
♪ Yet they never buried this ♪

131
00:08:35,549 --> 00:08:38,880
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

132
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:41,320
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

133
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:43,799
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

134
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:48,120
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

135
00:08:49,050 --> 00:08:53,060
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

136
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,390
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

137
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,200
Li,

138
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:57,750
from now on,

139
00:08:57,770 --> 00:08:57,920
I will be yours and yours alone.

140
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:00,320
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

141
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,550
The world is vast.

142
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,390
Wherever you want to go,

143
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:06,080
I will follow you.

144
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:06,970
Zhao, no matter how vast the world is,

145
00:09:06,970 --> 00:09:09,200
[Chunliu Garden]

146
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,960
having you by my side is all I need.
